<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ر ا:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهِرَاوَةُ)</span> بِالْكَسْرِ الْعَصَا الضَّخْمَةُ وَالْجَمْعُ <span class="c2">(الْهَرَاوَى)</span> بِفَتْحِ الْهَاءِ وَالْوَاوِ. وَ <span class="c2">(هَرَاةُ)</span> اسْمُ بَلَدٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>